<h2>🔥 Characteristics of Chemical Change</h2>

<ul>

<li>Heat produced 🔥</li>

<li>Gas produced 💨</li>

<li>Color change 🎨</li>

<li>Precipitate formed ⚗️</li>

</ul>

Example: Rusting of iron

</div>

<div class="card">

<h2>⚙️ Characteristics of Physical Change</h2>

<ul>

<li>No new substance formed</li>

<li>Usually reversible</li>

<li>Only shape/size/state change</li>

</ul>

Example: Ice melting

</div>

